overview: Beginning as a long term project to list absolutely everything in the known and unknown universes, You Tube phenomenon Alasdair Tremblay-Birchall's roster of everything from pork chops, violin lessons, to people who pronounce the word ‘film’ as ‘FILL-LUHM’ is as strangely silly as it is oddly compelling. A true original.
title: Alasdair Tremblay-Birchall: Alasdair Lists Everything
